         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Cope Cope ¶  April 11. 1888. ¶ Baron von Mueller. ¶ Esteemed Sir. ¶  ¶ With this mail I venture to send you a plant for whose definition I would like to kindly ask you. It is generally accepted here t...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="de">88.04.11</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="de">From Rudolph Camerer</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="de">RB MSS M1, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Found with a specimen of <seg style="font-style: italic; ">Chamaesyce drummondii</seg> (MEL 2178965). MS annotation by M: 'Answ. 14/4/88'; letter not found.</p>
               </note>Cope Cope April 11. 88.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Baron von Muller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">Geehrter Herr.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <seg style="">
                  <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Mit dieser Post erlaube ich mir Ihnen eine Pflanze zuzuschicken um deren definition Ich Sie gefälligst bitten möchte. Es ist hier allgemein angenommen, dass diese Pflanze es ist, die so viele Schafe vergiftet, so dass </seg>
               <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">namentlich hungrige</hi>
               </seg>
               <seg style=""> Schafe, die nicht an diese Weide gewöhnt sind, in grosser Anzahl binnen 20 Minuten nach Genuss sterben. L. Brown Esqr. of this place hat sehr viele verloren. Gefällige Antwort entgegensehend</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">Ihr achtungsvoll</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="de">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>R. Camerer.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg style="">Cope Cope</seg>
               <note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">Vic. MS annotation by M: 'via Ballarat'.</p>
               </note>
               <seg style=""> April 11. 1888.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Esteemed Sir.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>With this mail I venture to send you a plant for whose definition I would like to kindly ask you. It is generally accepted here that it is this plant that poisons so many sheep, so that <seg style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">particularly hungry</hi>
               </seg> sheep that are not used to this pasture die in large numbers within 20 minutes after eating. L. Brown Esqr. of this place has lost very many. Anticipating a helpful answer</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Your respectful</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; font-size: 10pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>R. Camerer.</p>
         </div>
